### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071
@instanceId = 

### 1. Ingestar documento de prueba - Tasación
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/IngestDocument
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instrucciones": {
    "expectedType": "Tasacion",
    "skipDuplicateCheck": false,
    "forceReprocess": false,
    "classification": {
      "model": "auto",
      "umbral": 0.85
    },
    "extraction": {
      "model": "auto",
      "umbral": 0.80
    }
  },
  "documento": {
    "name": "tasacion_test_001.pdf",
    "content": {
      "base64": ""
    }
  },
  "trazabilidad": {
    "correlationId": "TEST-001-2026",
    "submittedBy": "usuario.prueba@sareb.es",
    "idGDC": null,
    "idActivo": "ACT-12345"
  }
}

### 2. Consultar estado de la orquestación
# Copia el instanceId de la respuesta anterior y reemplázalo arriba en @instanceId
GET {{baseUrl}}/runtime/webhooks/durabletask/instances/{{instanceId}}

### 3. Obtener resultado completo
GET {{baseUrl}}/runtime/webhooks/durabletask/instances/{{instanceId}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. Purgar historial de instancia
POST {{baseUrl}}/runtime/webhooks/durabletask/instances/{{instanceId}}/purge

### 5. Test con Skip Duplicate Check
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/IngestDocument
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instrucciones": {
    "expectedType": "Tasacion",
    "skipDuplicateCheck": true,
    "forceReprocess": true,
    "classification": {
      "model": "DI",
      "umbral": 0.90
    },
    "extraction": {
      "model": "GPT",
      "umbral": 0.75
    }
  },
  "documento": {
    "name": "tasacion_test_002.pdf",
    "content": {
      "base64": ""
    }
  },
  "trazabilidad": {
    "correlationId": "TEST-002-2026",
    "submittedBy": "usuario.prueba@sareb.es",
    "idGDC": "GDC-98765",
    "idActivo": "ACT-67890"
  }
}

### 6. Listar todas las instancias
GET {{baseUrl}}/runtime/webhooks/durabletask/instances

### 7. Terminar orquestación manualmente
POST {{baseUrl}}/runtime/webhooks/durabletask/instances/{{instanceId}}/terminate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Prueba terminada manualmente"
}
